attributes.background:
Given the never-ending stream of CDs, DVDs and laptops being lost by Government departments containing our personal data, this petition demands that:-

a) ALL data being transported be encrypted to the highest possible levels;

b) data NOT be transported by any means, nor stored on laptops, unless it can be shown to be ABSOLUTELY necessary;

c) in cases where the movement of data is necessary, it be carried out either in person or by REGISTERED courier;

d) the Government take full responsibility for the financial consequences of the loss of any data, and those responsible face prosecution under the Data Protection Act.
